# Weather App

## Overview

This project is a simple weather application that allows users to check the current temperature and weather description for a given city. The app fetches data from the WeatherAPI.com service.

## Features

- Real-time weather data
- Responsive design
- Search by city name
- Implemented with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Easy to integrate and customize

## Preview

![Weather App Preview](./preview.png)

## Usage

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/WaqasArshad97/weather-app.git


Open the index.html file in a web browser.

Enter a city name in the input field and click the "Search" button.

View the real-time temperature and weather description for the specified city.

## API Key
To use the WeatherAPI.com service, you need to obtain an API key. Replace 'YOUR_API_KEY' in script.js with your actual API key. Get your API key from `WeatherAPI.com`.

## Customization
You can customize the Weather App's appearance or behavior by modifying the HTML, CSS, and JavaScript files. Feel free to experiment with different styles, add additional features, or integrate it into your existing projects.

